{"tid":2173343,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫護界多人拒全民檢測   專家推斷參與率僅三成","createTime":"2020-08-25T07:34:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T11:51:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b3fd15c683ae0f8052bdb975507ae9ba00396079","tid":2173343,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T07:34:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200825/LBFCRQKJSBA5BFIZB4WC5ND7GM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200825%2FLBFCRQKJSBA5BFIZB4WC5ND7GM%2F&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXfsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=e1613ff8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200825%2FLBFCRQKJSBA5BFIZB4WC5ND7GM%2F&h=4cb11c08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200825/LBFCRQKJSBA5BFIZB4WC5ND7GM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n醫護界多人拒全民檢測  <br />\n專家推斷參與率僅三成<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pATJKZUj5CbVxuTO0si1xMI7uGY=/2658x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JN2FN5QTGZHHNF2FHN5LFVHZNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpATJKZUj5CbVxuTO0si1xMI7uGY%3D%2F2658x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJN2FN5QTGZHHNF2FHN5LFVHZNY.jpg&h=7d4838f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港府強推全民檢測，專家指市民參與率不會多於三成。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【武肺再爆發】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：聶德權推翻陳肇始 驗毒解禁不掛鈎<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港疫情逐步回落，惟中央堅持動員大批內地人員來港強推全民檢測，多名醫護及專家直言不會接受病毒檢測，部份明言不信任政府的計劃，對計劃更大潑冷水，西醫工會會長楊超發料僅三成市民參與，認為政府要派超市禮券始可增吸引力，港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良指全民檢測成效低，料只能發現約40名隱形患者，與政府預計社區有1,500名隱形患者的推算相差甚遠 。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良昨接受電台訪問時明言，自己受感染機會微乎其微，不會接受檢測，「放。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ATUW5EUdBmyPoo4NoO1Sl6ZTQQo=/1928x1216/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/M2IXYWLEKNDLRMX2UVUQJDDDDM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FATUW5EUdBmyPoo4NoO1Sl6ZTQQo%3D%2F1928x1216%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FM2IXYWLEKNDLRMX2UVUQJDDDDM.gif&h=1bcf4203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何栢良料僅找出40隱形患者<br />\n<br />\n何認為全民檢測成效低，高危群組循環檢測的防疫效果反而較大，當局應加快推行。他指政府估算高峯期社區有1,500個隱形患者，但預計至9月初，隱形患者數目會隨疫情回落，若有300萬人參與，相信亦只能找出約40名隱形患者。<br />\n<br />\n楊超發指，政府於慈雲山等高危地區推行的檢測，參與率僅約三成，相信全民檢測參與度不會高於此數，認為政府需提供誘因吸。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n本報昨查詢多名醫護及專家會否接受檢測，大部份表明拒絕。醫學會會長蔡堅坦言：「覺得冇需要。」。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n呼吸系統科專科醫生梁子超批評政府全民檢測放棄深喉唾液，改為拭子採樣是最大敗筆，「拭子採樣要大量人手，市民又。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不過，政府專家顧問、中大呼吸系統學講座教授許樹昌表明參加，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭︰醫生政客抹黑計劃<br />\n<br />\n另一位表明會接受檢測的感染及傳染病專科醫生曾祈殷解釋，「。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另方面，建制派近日總動員號召，其中工聯會在facebook專頁呼籲42萬名。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭昨晚亦在fb指社會上有小部份人不斷抹黑計劃，「。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"ddc377c6a7c6cc4a94f8566d1da346a44d51a9b0","tid":2173343,"uid":289978,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T07:40:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DXTpLf4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDXTpLf4.jpg&h=35055929&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n全港藍屍曱甴全力擁護三低政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b0ff07d1bd18c9038462781d4b14334e21ca03","tid":2173343,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T07:41:15.000Z","msg":"症苦: 醫護政治化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0b7fa234bcf755f25506702ab932565cb7ad6f","tid":2173343,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T07:42:10.000Z","msg":"三成 = 200萬人"},{"pid":"f5f026844c62fd73a836775ec0b3d1a53108d21e","tid":2173343,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T07:43:43.000Z","msg":"有 70萬 unique 既人擋佢贏"},{"pid":"9d043ca3cdf543667cc919f6ce48d6e1